tool_description: Site economics - average residential buy and rent price of a location
name: Real estate value
title: Real estate value

api_list.name: /get_residential_buy_rent_rates
api_list.description: The rent and buy rates for residential properties is predicted as an average of the rates within an area about the central point of the given location. Location can be given as lat + lng, geohash, h3 index or an address. Rate is returned in Rupees per square foot.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://real-estate-value.p.rapidapi.com/get_residential_buy_rent_rates"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "real-estate-value.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
